file.name: main.yml.tmpl
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: "{{ $.Name }} Demo"
  description: ""
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
- url: /{{ $.Name }}
paths:
  /health:
    get:
      tags:
      - health
      summary: API health check
      operationId: healthCheck
      parameters:
      - name: type
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
          enum:
          - liveness
          - readiness
      responses:
        200:
          description: Success
          content: {}
        404:
          description: unknown check type
          content: {}
components:
  schemas:
    BaseDefaultRes:
      type: object
    BadRequestRes:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
